That is still too much.
I propose we cut down Mac and Windows even more. Most apps run on Linux, AIX, *BSD, Mac (Server) and because we are not using native functions, this should not have an impact.

Proposal:
* Just one build of Java 8 and Java 17 for each Platform Windows and Mac
* Leave the Linux builds untouched.
